rm睇片"},{"pid":"99935f530c8d11101d612194b13732913f021164","tid":30524,"uid":59494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T10:52:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6-_4Uoo_7Y4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6-_4Uoo_7Y4&d=QUtA3jpSdi2dF0VVywYy0wT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=24357ca9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6-_4Uoo_7Y4</a><br />\n<br />\n懶人包:<br />\n佢發現最近youtube有三個多左出黎嘅features:<br />\n1. 會自動unsub youtube channel<br />\n2. 即使自己sub左嘅channel 都唔一定會出現係homepage<br />\n3. Homepage一定係俾Trending個堆youtube video佔據<br />\n<br />\n其實尾個兩個現象都好似FB(like左page都唔俾你睇佢啲post，同埋會塞啲佢想佢俾你睇嘅野多過自己想睇嘅野)<br />\n<br />\n佢就send左email去yt，但係無正面回應<br />\n<br />\n然後佢又發現自己嘅片views數少左好多，但係自己又覺得個啲片係<span style=\"color: red;\">高質</span>嘅，留言個啲人都話啲片高質，所以佢就將呢個現象嘅原因當係1-3<br />\n<br />\n佢就話youtube嘅最終目的係搵另一個(堆)人取代自己 因為自己雄霸得太耐，而但係youtube想推上位個堆人整個啲片又好低質<br />\n<br />\n佢睇唔過眼，所以想係達到50M sub嘅時候delete左個channel，重新黎過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n雖然係事實 但咁樣同youtube講又有得串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢發現咗11月開始D新片views明顯比10月低<br />\n睇analysis原來嚟自&quot;suggested video&quot;嘅views由佔30%-40%跌到0.X％<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即係話Youtube近來冇將佢D新片suggest畀人 (而家成個frontpage都係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"},{"pid":"8a4be346f3ec65b07f6cdcef000b0244ec0600b2","tid":30524,"uid":33070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T10:53:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6ad1f247e9d54a0f0f9420653261d81980742894","tid":30524,"uid":4206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T10:56:36.000Z","msg":"而家YouTube推薦影片成日都有啲殘體字標題嘅片<br />\n話咗不感興趣都仲係咁彈出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5b28665ef729a0c2a9892c54b4c0ba4ef27f